{"tid":1492725,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"高普：我們負擔不起古天奴(嘴抽筋)　當日勸留隊一席話成神預言","createTime":"2019-08-21T03:10:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T04:06:06.000Z","uid":73381,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0ce6c8109548949534a0615f72bab2af5922a606","tid":1492725,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T03:10:01.000Z","msg":"古天奴如願加盟巴塞，可是在加泰隆尼亞的18個月並不如意，一直踢不出在利物浦時期的最佳水平，他以借將身份加盟拜仁後，不禁令人想起高普當時力勸古天奴留隊的神預言：「留在這裏，他們將會為你立像表揚你的成就；加盟其他球隊，去巴塞隆拿、去拜仁慕尼黑、去皇家馬德里，你不過是另一個球員。留在這裏你可以得到更多。」<br />\n<br />\n高普原句：&quot;Stay here and they will end up building a statue in your honour. Go somewhere else, to Barcelona, to Bayern Munich, to Real Madrid, and you will be just another player. Here you can be something more.&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E9%AB%94%E8%82%B2/365892/%E8%B6%B3%E7%90%83-%E9%AB%98%E6%99%AE-%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E8%B2%A0%E6%93%94%E4%B8%8D%E8%B5%B7%E5%8F%A4%E5%A4%A9%E5%A5%B4-%E7%95%B6%E6%97%A5%E5%8B%B8%E7%95%99%E9%9A%8A%E4%B8%80%E5%B8%AD%E8%A9%B1%E6%88%90%E7%A5%9E%E9%A0%90%E8%A8%80\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E9%25AB%2594%25E8%2582%25B2%2F365892%2F%25E8%25B6%25B3%25E7%2590%2583-%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2599%25AE-%25E6%2588%2591%25E5%2580%2591%25E8%25B2%25A0%25E6%2593%2594%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E5%258F%25A4%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E5%25A5%25B4-%25E7%2595%25B6%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%258B%25B8%25E7%2595%2599%25E9%259A%258A%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25B8%25AD%25E8%25A9%25B1%25E6%2588%2590%25E7%25A5%259E%25E9%25A0%2590%25E8%25A8%2580&d=DXuv2gayA%2Byyjyt3RGK41CWBa%2BgBXVTVyFCVgu0cTpM%3D&h=89d90790\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E9%AB%94%E8%82%B2/365892/%E8%B6%B3%E7%90%83-%E9%AB%98%E6%99%AE-%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E8%B2%A0%E6%93%94%E4%B8%8D%E8%B5%B7%E5%8F%A4%E5%A4%A9%E5%A5%B4-%E7%95%B6%E6%97%A5%E5%8B%B8%E7%95%99%E9%9A%8A%E4%B8%80%E5%B8%AD%E8%A9%B1%E6%88%90%E7%A5%9E%E9%A0%90%E8%A8%80</a>"},{"pid":"4